Package es.weso.asio.ontology.test.manifest

Interface ManifestParser

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ManifestParserImpl
    public interface ManifestParser
    The manifest parser reads a manifest file and extracts the array of test cases that it defines. It is composed by a default constructor that takes the path to the manifest file and a getTestCases method that parses the given file and returns an array of test cases.
    Author:
    Guillermo Facundo Colunga
